    <h1>Privacy Policy – The Gold Blessing</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 22, 2025</p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>This application automates posting of product images, videos, and content to The Gold Blessing Facebook Page. It is operated by SoleBlessing Ventures Corporation.</p>

    <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Facebook Page access tokens (stored securely in Google Apps Script)</li>
        <li>Content metadata (product names, prices, captions, hashtags)</li>
        <li>Engagement metrics (likes, shares, comments) for analytics purposes</li>
        <li>Post timestamps and performance data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Post content to your Facebook Page</li>
        <li>Track engagement metrics to optimize posting times</li>
        <li>Maintain access tokens for continuous automation</li>
        <li>Generate logs for debugging and performance monitoring</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>All access tokens and logs are stored within Google Apps Script and Google Sheets, accessible only by authorized admins. No third-party service outside of Facebook and Google processes your data. Meta Platforms Inc. and Google LLC process data independently under their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share data with any external parties.</p>

    <h2>Rights and Removal</h2>
    <p>Admins who wish to revoke access may:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Remove the TGB Channels (Official AI) app from Facebook Business Integrations, or</li>
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:inquiry@soleblessing.com">inquiry@soleblessing.com</a> to request complete deletion of data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to comply with new requirements. The revised version will be posted here with a new "Last Updated" date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
